Aloha President Kouchi, Speaker Nakamura, and Members of the Legislature:
This is to inform you that on June 25, 2026, the following bill was signed into law:
S.B. NO. 2721, S.D. 1, H.D. 1, RELATING TO THE ADMINISTRATION OF
