13 section 15 of Act 19, Session Laws of Hawaii 2020; and
14 (2) The amendments made to section 709-906(19), Hawaii
15 Revised Statutes, by section 19 of this Act shall not
16 be repealed when that section is reenacted on June 30,
17 2026, pursuant to section 4 of Act 238, Session Laws
18 of Hawaii 2021.
